{"tid":524402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭 算唔算香港最佳特首?","createTime":"2018-01-09T14:12:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T14:31:31.000Z","uid":76855,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7a64b6f29102afe8c1171374ceaee5cfb92a0103","tid":524402,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:12:25.000Z","msg":"【認真巴弊】林鄭親邀阿里來港上市<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥一向支持同股不同權，去年上任不久便到訪杭州與阿里巴巴主席馬雲會面，證監會與港交所(388)早前亦落實今年中在主板，為新經濟企業推行同股不同權，實行希望吸引馬雲旗下企業重回香港市場上市。<br />\n<br />\n今晚在浙商總會晚宴上，林鄭月娥直接向馬雲「拉生意」，表示「希望阿里巴巴重返香港上市」。馬雲即場回應指：「會認真考慮在香港的市場」，又指不會辜負林鄭月娥及香港，會幫助香港成為繼紐約後第二大金融市場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好積極做事 為香港好<br />\n<br />\n環球科技巨企落戶香江<br />\n<br />\n真心唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0e703c8066037ffb076b622256c2a201e45c4d","tid":524402,"uid":28113,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:20:44.000Z","msg":"一定係歷屆最佳女特首㗎"},{"pid":"3b55cd773154508845501e145ca1bb86236acec7","tid":524402,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:23:37.000Z","msg":"得一個點都係最佳嫁啦"},{"pid":"518ee0d1796bf2726ab4d2411afe4dc4906e69a5","tid":524402,"uid":155568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4978e37fb80495f04a33e37b4a113f11e3626afc","tid":524402,"uid":78039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"518ee0d1796bf2726ab4d2411afe4dc4906e69a5","tid":524402,"uid":155568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:31:06.000Z","msg":"好波, 港膠所一定好開心"},{"pid":"9a3029d4727f0a81c771f0332fcd2bb9ec2cd9a9","tid":524402,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"518ee0d1796bf2726ab4d2411afe4dc4906e69a5","tid":524402,"uid":155568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪